Grizmo might seem perplexing /pəˈpleksɪŋ 费解的/,

23
00:01:04,973 --> 00:01:07,060
in the wild, these same behaviors,

24
00:01:07,060 --> 00:01:10,188
naturally bred into cats 
for millions of years,

25
00:01:10,188 --> 00:01:13,377
