from the top of the bookcase

32
00:01:34,357 --> 00:01:37,911
is exactly what she has evolved to do.

33
00:01:37,911 --> 00:01:44,122
As wild predators, cats are opportunistic /ˌɒpətjʊˈnɪstɪk 机会主义的/
and hunt whenever prey is available.

34
00:01:44,122 --> 00:01:45,980
Since most cat prey are small,

35
00:01:45,980 --> 00:01:49,651
cats in the wild needed to eat 
many times each day,

36
00:01:49,651 --> 00:01:54,991
and use a stalk /stɔːk 追踪/, pounce /paʊns 猛扑/, kill, eat
strategy to stay fed.

37
00:01:54,991 --> 00:01:58,862
This is why Grizmo prefers to chase
and pounce on little toys

38
00:01:58,862 --> 00:02:02,860
