of the day and night.

39
00:02:02,860 --> 00:02:08,141
Also, small prey tend to hide in tiny
spaces in their natural environments,

40
00:02:08,141 --> 00:02:12,541
so one explanation /ˌɛkspləˈneɪʃən/ for Grizmo's propensity /prəˈpɛnsɪtɪ 习性/
to reach into containers and openings

