predominate /prɪˈdɒmɪˌneɪt 主宰/ behaviors

66
00:03:31,789 --> 00:03:34,292
is still one of the most mysterious /mɪˈstɪərɪəs/.

67
00:03:34,292 --> 00:03:37,623
Cats may purr for any number of reasons,

68
00:03:37,623 --> 00:03:38,809
