tissue regeneration /rɪˌdʒɛnəˈreɪʃən 再生/.

74
00:03:51,292 --> 00:03:54,777
So while her purring makes Grizmo
an excellent /ˈɛksələnt 出色的/ nap /næp 小睡/ companion /kəmˈpænjən 同伴/,

75
00:03:54,777 --> 00:04:00,118
