is healing /hiːl 治愈/ her muscles and bones,

76
00:04:00,118 --> 00:04:03,265
and maybe even yours, too.

77
00:04:03,265 --> 00:04:04,627
They developed through time

78
00:04:04,627 --> 00:04:07,752
as both solitary /ˈsɒlɪtərɪ 独居的/ predators 
that hunted and killed to eat,

79
00:04:07,752 --> 00:04:12,063
and stealthy /ˈstelθɪ 鬼鬼祟祟的/ prey that hid
and escaped to survive.

80
00:04:12,063 --> 00:04:15,245
So cats today retain many 
of the same instincts /instiŋkt 本能/

81
00:04:15,245 --> 00:04:19,686
